### Create a new question
POST http://localhost:9192/api/questions/create-new-question
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the capital of France?",
  "subject": "Geography",
  "questionType": "MCQ",
  "choices": ["Paris", "London", "Berlin", "Rome"],
  "correctAnswers": ["Paris"]
}

### Get all questions
GET http://localhost:9192/api/questions/all-questions

### Get question by ID
GET http://localhost:9192/api/questions/question/1

### Update a question
PUT http://localhost:9192/api/questions/question/1/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the capital of Germany?",
  "subject": "Geography",
  "questionType": "MCQ",
  "choices": ["Paris", "London", "Berlin", "Rome"],
  "correctAnswers": ["Berlin"]
}

### Delete a question
DELETE http://localhost:9192/api/questions/question/1/delete

### Get all subjects
GET http://localhost:9192/api/questions/subjects

### Fetch random questions for user
GET http://localhost:9192/api/questions/quiz/fetch-questions-for-user?numOfQuestions=1&subject=Geography